name: ABDUCTED (itch) (FlashCash0402)
description:
You are abducted by martians, and you wake up in a glitchy simulation that loops by space & time. Can u beat their silly simulation in all 4 dimensions?

They run you through different sets of tests, to test various abilities of the so called "lowly" earthlings.

Can we prove them wrong? Or will we be forced to accepting their supremacy?
